/*/
//------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Method GetAllSchemas() Class tgvSchemas
	oRest:setKeyHeaderResponse('Content-Type','application/json')
	oRest:setStatusCode(200)
	oRest:setResponse(::oService:GetAllSchemas())
return .T.
